&lt;p&gt;Now we can safely reuse the &lt;code&gt;fib&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; function and reduce its time complexity to $O(n)$.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Notably, if you still want the original naive pure recursive version of fib, you can still build it as:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
